sequenceDiagram
    actor U as User / Judge
    participant UI as Frontend Dashboard
    participant API as Flask API
    participant TW as DigitalTwin
    participant AD as AnomalyDetector
    participant MCP as MCP Server (Orchestrator)
    participant T1 as Tool 1: Ticket Search
    participant T2 as Tool 2: BOM Lookup
    participant T3 as Tool 3: Design-Doc RAG
    participant T4 as Tool 4: Past-Fix Retrieval
    participant LLM as Gemini Client

    U->>UI: Click "Run 4-Tool MCP Agent"
    UI->>API: POST /api/analyze_rca {query, use_llm}
    API->>TW: snapshot()
    TW-->>API: telemetry state
    API->>AD: detect(snapshot)
    AD-->>API: [Finding(signal, failure_mode, confidence)]
    API->>MCP: run_rca_pipeline(query, use_llm)

    MCP->>T1: tool_ticket_search(query, top_k=5)
    T1-->>MCP: similar tickets + similarity scores
    MCP->>MCP: infer failure_mode from top matches

    MCP->>T2: tool_bom_lookup(failure_mode)
    T2-->>MCP: BOM spec cross-reference

    MCP->>T3: tool_design_doc_search(query, top_k=3)
    T3-->>MCP: design guideline documents

    MCP->>T4: tool_past_fix_retrieval(failure_mode, top_k=3)
    T4-->>MCP: validated fixes ranked by effectiveness

    alt Gemini configured and reachable
        MCP->>LLM: synthesize_with_gemini(context)
        LLM-->>MCP: cited narrative report
    else No key / network / quota failure
        MCP->>MCP: synthesize_rule_based(context)
        Note over MCP: Never blocks the demo -\ndeterministic grounded fallback
    end

    MCP-->>API: {trace, synthesis, citations, latency_ms}
    API-->>UI: JSON response
    UI-->>U: Renders live reasoning trace + cited report
